description: Water views await, this is top floor living at its best! With its incredibly convenient location (1 block to soon to be revamped Heights, 2 blocks to Broadway, 3 blocks to beach), you'll have the best of Southie's dining, nightlife, & retail scene at your fingertips, plus EZ access to the Red Line. Ascend the private staircase to a versatile, sunplashed floorplan with gleaming hardwood floors, neutral tones, & windows in all the right places. The open kitchen / living area has elegant crown molding, & recessed lighting. Modern kitchen w/ handsome cabinetry, tile backsplash, S/S appliances, & a large granite peninsula w bar seating. Slider to a brand new trex deck with gorgeous water views. Spiral staircase to a brand new roof remains for you to build out the roof deck of your dreams and capture some of the finest views in the neighborhood! Both BRs have walk-in closets, incl primary with massive space that could also function as an office nook. W/D, AC, xtra storage. The total package!
